# Islamly - Comprehensive Islamic Learning Platform

**Your Comprehensive Islamic Learning Platform - Salafi/Athari Methodology**

## Overview

Islamly is a comprehensive Islamic learning platform built with modern web technologies, rooted in Salafi/Athari methodology.

## Features

- Quran Module with translations, tafsir, and audio
- Hadith Studies with grading and chains of narration
- Fiqh & Rulings with evidence-based approach
- Aqeedah based on Quran, Sunnah, and Salaf
- AI-Powered Learning
- Islamic Calendar with prayer times
- Community Features

## Tech Stack

- Next.js 14 (App Router)
- TypeScript 5
- Tailwind CSS 3
- Zustand
- Prisma ORM
- NextAuth.js

## Getting Started

```bash
npm install
npm run dev
```

Open http://localhost:3000

## Project Structure

```
islamly/
├── src/
│   ├── app/           # Next.js pages
│   ├── components/    # React components
│   ├── lib/          # Utilities
│   ├── store/        # Zustand stores
│   ├── hooks/        # Custom hooks
│   ├── types/        # TypeScript types
│   └── services/     # API services
├── prisma/           # Database
└── public/           # Static assets
```

## Modules

1. Quran (1-200)
2. Tafsir (201-300)
3. Hadith (301-500)
4. Aqeedah (501-600)
5. Fiqh (601-700)
6. AI Tools (701-800)
7. Learning Systems (801-900)
8. Community (901-1000)

